{"tid":429523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢比人鬧要反省","createTime":"2017-10-09T03:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T08:28:22.000Z","uid":91326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"169d963dded6447c595d8fa23096a8c20d83667a","tid":429523,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"話就一向發夢 都係笑下就算 有時奇奇怪怪既會同女朋友講 然後大家都笑下 開心下 我諗都係好正常既事 個個都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但今日發夢話發到佢同其他男仔一齊 點點點 之後佢就話我痴線 仲話我成日係咁 真係要反省一下 做咩成日發咁既夢 <br />\n<br />\n我笑左 原來發夢都係做錯野既一種 要反省 但佢之前又試過發我同個醜女係埋一齊 然後講出黎笑我 我都當講笑咁<br />\n但家下就走黎鬧我 叫我反省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家評評理啦<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發夢姐 反省d咩啊 佢就要反省啦<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你潛意識咁先會發咁既夢 反省下啦你"},{"pid":"468a83afaef63d4de09929e95f788f0b541db6e0","tid":429523,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"仲話驚我夜晚會砍死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae31565c76c024e1e376e181fdaac78669febbcf","tid":429523,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cbbc293c336219fa1f6bc8d3a7db3ed37096f94e","tid":429523,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ee9ecbd93385a3a22d818dfb4cd2f987f3c30309","tid":429523,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"發夢姐 反省d咩啊 佢就要反省啦"},{"pid":"a14a09b8778e4bfed06562798ef357f82b8dd5ba","tid":429523,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09